Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.47,0:00:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名為伊澤爾坎特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.37,0:00:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘在此宣佈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式開始侵略地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫蒂 孩子們拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 上來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們去哪兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啟動高達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 救世主登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.54,0:00:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…高達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又與我作對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他從上面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星移民計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其失敗被遺留在火星圈的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.37,0:01:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱獨立國家維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球聯邦政府宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭開始 已近70年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和其他機動戰士完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛艙裏的是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特·明日野嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但另一個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 天神號能改變戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想辦法堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是我們的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會放棄的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德比克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪克 振作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群該死的恐龍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利巴諾茲仍在交戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各城市損失加劇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與總司令部恢復聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放影像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好您在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾倫格雷亞斯提督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說這種情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 從現在起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落·樓蘭就是聯邦軍的新指揮部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須粉碎維甘及伊澤爾坎特的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾倫格雷亞斯提督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧利巴諾茲 3號線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督 我想應該讓您知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方纔 前總司令菲利特·明日野來電
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前總司令來電？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 要求出動動態保養中的天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是那位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也無權指揮軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下打算拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即出動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動天神號！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令有他的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪克的駕駛艙蓋被卡住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快安排營救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然無視前線的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.32,0:06:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻優先退役軍官的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種老舊戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動也不會有所作為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 火燒眉毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我哪裏去找一船乘員？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一些問題兵源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那艘船正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下只有阿比斯隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就它了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是總司令部的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差艦長了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試有意思的人選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠老爸陞遷的官二代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會馬上好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 溫蒂姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納圖爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 媽媽她們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幫忙找避難所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒著也是閒著 我們玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我想去看機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較喜歡這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納圖爾·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令找你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去當天神號艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你能勝任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是上尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠格當艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火線任命你從今天起晉陞少校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有參加艦船指揮的研修課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有實踐經驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我一直在做基地內勤…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你告訴我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是情況危機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要你這樣的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是艾娜斯中將的孫女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有做不到的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很配明日野老司令的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要振作！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是天神號的艦長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下納圖爾·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是機動戰士隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊命令已經下達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛被提拔為艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有自信是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子戴歪了 說明穿不慣艦長服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子系得太緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想隱瞞自信心的缺乏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 關係到大家的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入艦橋時 無須寒暄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃… 是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利小姐比較較真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不反感寒暄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話大聲說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 伊桑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 先讓我填飽肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這份是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 啟航準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟航 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退開 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏了結你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法·澤奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘沒有人性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人不眨眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是奧利巴諾茲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是駕駛高達的菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫納圖爾·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你該明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是反擊的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你該明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是反擊的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是…反擊的關鍵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯隊等你的指示呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會打仗的人 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長這樣 前途堪憂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩台機體完成維護可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德雷克 奧布萊特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.55,0:14:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 滅了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助天神號扭轉戰局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿比斯隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 準備好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊落敵人母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊落母艦是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要發射光子爆破炮嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那東西破壞力太強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大氣層內不能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投射高達的新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！沒有啟動AGE系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統的話已經啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是洛蒂·麥德納
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出動天神號是為了AGE系統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才一直在試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有出錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造新武器的戰鬥數據不足
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 動手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把設計系統的報警等級降至30以下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行完成構築
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不知會造出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 快照辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有新武器能扭轉乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有新武器 就能擊落母艦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還得看你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅持到武器完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達緩口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起高達歸我指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說什麼 我們獨立行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是菲利特·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您已經退伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 現在需要互相協助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事的話 兩台一起幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去迂迴背面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新兵器的構築還沒完成嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附件大幅提高了西格瑪希斯步槍的輸出功率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子相當危險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留意裝填時間比較長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器代號 魔道加農
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是小型光子環陣列
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:18:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用步槍光束射出附件積聚的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量充填
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 集火高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要打…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.49,0:20:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造出這麼個怪物兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 輕易動用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野老司令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隊長 舍利奇·阿比斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.62,0:20:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.81,0:20:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼離開我們的隊列
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們的防禦沒有信心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艦長納圖爾·艾娜斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦即將前往新設總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失落·樓蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法發揮艦船實力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不配當艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.77,0:21:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長擔負著全船人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你信得過高達嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達回應了我的操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.86,0:21:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特是維甘的首領吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他是邪惡的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想毀滅人類的魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要消滅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅那些傷天害理的維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺的高達
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙漠的亡靈逼近艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上戰鬥之路的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.88,0:24:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的覺悟受到挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.43,0:24:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰慄 沙漠的亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.57,0:24:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號已經成為老舊艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.94,0:24:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是經過多次改修
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.86,0:24:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然擁有不輸第一線戰艦的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力強大的光子爆破炮也健在

